@startuml
left to right direction
actor User
rectangle "Browse Module" as Browse
rectangle "Messaging Module" as Msg
rectangle "Ad Module" as Ad
database "DB" as DB
User -> Browse: search/filter
Browse -> DB: query profiles
DB --> Browse: profiles
User -> Msg: view conversations
Msg -> DB: fetch conversations/messages
DB --> Msg: conversation data
User -> Ad: create draft
Ad -> DB: save draft
@enduml